\emph default
 
\begin_inset Formula $D=V_{{\scriptscriptstyle \text{MAX}}}-V_{{\scriptscriptstyle \text{MIN}}}$
\end_inset

 (poniamo 
\begin_inset Formula $D=10V$
\end_inset

